summary: Mesh replacer for Khajiit race to make Khajiits faces more catlike.
descriptionHtml:
THIS IS NOT MY MOD, IT ENTIRELY BELONGS TO ZALUNAYA.
<br />
<br />I recently noticed that the original upload of this mod was deleted from the Nexus, so I felt like I had to re-upload it.
<br />
<br />I saw this mod In a Brodual showcase and thought it looked cool, but when I clicked on the link to the Nexus the file was missing. I was able to find the file in a Reddit thread with a link to Google drive, so I simply placed that file in this upload.
<br />
<br />I am by no means a modder! I just uploaded the file as it was after downloading it via Google drive.
<br />
author: Zalunaya
